    • Uses of CatanModel in server.command

      Methods in server.command that return CatanModel 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      CatanModel YearOfPlentyCommand.execute()
      Executes "Year of Plenty Dev Card", removes the dev card from the players hand.
      CatanModel SoldierCommand.execute()
      Executes "Soldier Dev Card", removes the dev card from the players hand.
      CatanModel SendChatCommand.execute()
      Executes "Send Chat", send the instigator's message to be broadcast to all other players
      CatanModel RollNumberCommand.execute()
      Executes "Roll Number", Randomly choose 2 numbers between 1 and 6, then sums them together.
      CatanModel RobPlayerCommand.execute()
      Executes "Rob Player", player picks from a list of robbable player.
      CatanModel RoadBuildingCommand.execute()
      Executes "Road Building Dev Card", removes the dev card from the players hand.
      CatanModel OfferTradeCommand.execute()
      Executes the "Offer Trade", Player specifies what he/she is will to give in exchanged for his/her specified offer.
      CatanModel MovesCommand.execute() 
      CatanModel MonumentCommand.execute()
      Executes "Monument Dev Card", removes the dev card from the players hand.
      CatanModel MonopolyCommand.execute()
      Executes "Monopoly Dev Card", removes the dev card from the players hand.
      CatanModel MaritimeTradeCommand.execute()
      Executes "Maritime Trade", subtracts the given resources from the instigator and add the get resources to the instigator.
      CatanModel FinishTurnCommand.execute()
      Executes "Finish Turn", ends the players turn and allows the next player to perform his or her turn.
      CatanModel DiscardCardCommand.execute()
      Executes "Discard Card", removes the assigned card(s) from the players hand
      CatanModel CopyOfSendChatCommand.execute()
      Executes "Send Chat", send the instigator's message to be broadcast to all other players
      CatanModel BuyDevCardCommand.execute()
      Executes "Buy Dev Card", subtracts the resources from the instigator, adds a dev card to the players hand, and decrease from the bank of dev cards
      CatanModel BuildSettlementCommand.execute()
      Executes "Build Settlement", subtracts the resources from the instigator subtracts a city from unbuilt settlement pool and places it on a vertex location
      CatanModel BuildRoadCommand.execute()
      Executes "Build Road", subtracts the resources from the instigator subtracts a road from unbuilt road pool and places it on a edge location
      CatanModel BuildCityCommand.execute()
      Executes "Build City", subtracts the resources from the instigator subtracts a city from unbuilt city pool and places it on a vertex location
      CatanModel AcceptTradeCommand.execute()
      Executes the "Accept Trade", exchanges the resources between the instigator and the investigator
